description: The Theories Exam skill provides a review of the major theories used in psychotherapy including Gestalt, Adlerian, cognitive-behavioral, person-centered, narrative, solution-focused, existential, transactional analysis, psychodynamic, and more.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, tell theories exam to get me information about transactional analysis

name: Theories Exam
shortDescription: The Theories Exam skill provides you with information about the major theories used in psychotherapy.
